   "options": "<div style=\"padding: 14px 16px; background: #fcfcfd; border: 1px solid #eaecf0; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.6; color: #475467;\">The information you give on this form will be entered into a computerised register operated by OPITO. The register is available to employers, prospective employers and training providers in the offshore petroleum industry worldwide so that they may verify your training records. OPITO will collect and process information relating to you in accordance with the terms of UK GDPR and other relevant data protection legislation. Our privacy notice is available from https://opito.com/privacy-policy. If you have any enquiries about the use of your data please contact the Data Protection Officer at OPITO, Minerva House, Bruntland Road, Portlethen, Aberdeen, Scotland AB12 4QL, e-mail: data.protection@opito.com.<br><br>PO Box, 500726, Block 2B, Room F07, Knowledge Park, Dubai, United Arab Emirates Telephone: +971(0)4 4458 482 E-mail: reception@opito.com</div>"
